  <span class="target" id="ecommerce-platform-oscommerce"></span><div class="section" id="oscommerce-store-integration">
<h1>osCommerce Store Integration<a class="headerlink" href="#oscommerce-store-integration" title="Permalink to this headline">Â¶</a></h1>
<ol class="arabic">
<li><p class="first">Download the <a class="reference external" href="http://addons.oscommerce.com/info/7669">osCommerce Curebit Add-On</a> package and unzip it to your
osCommerce catalog directory (eg /var/www/oscommerce/catalog).</p>
</li>
<li><ul class="first">
<li><p class="first">For <strong>version 2.3</strong>, in your catalog directory, edit <em>checkout_success.php</em>
and replace this code:</p>
<div class="highlight-html"><div class="highlight"><pre>  <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">&quot;buttonSet&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;span</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">&quot;buttonAction&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><span class="cp">&lt;?php echo tep_draw_button(IMAGE_BUTTON_CONTINUE, &#39;triangle-1-e&#39;, null, &#39;primary&#39;); ?&gt;</span><span class="nt">&lt;/span&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;/form&gt;</span>

<span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="cp">  require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;template_bottom.php&#39;);</span>
<span class="cp">  require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;application_bottom.php&#39;);</span>
<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
<p>With this code:</p>
<div class="highlight-html"><div class="highlight"><pre>  <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">&quot;buttonSet&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;span</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">&quot;buttonAction&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span><span class="cp">&lt;?php echo tep_draw_button(IMAGE_BUTTON_CONTINUE, &#39;triangle-1-e&#39;, null, &#39;primary&#39;); ?&gt;</span><span class="nt">&lt;/span&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;/form&gt;</span>

<span class="c">&lt;!-- Begin Curebit integration code --&gt;</span>
<span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="cp">  include(DIR_WS_MODULES . &#39;order_total/curebit_checkout.php&#39;);</span>
<span class="cp">  if (class_exists(&#39;curebit_checkout&#39;)) {</span>
<span class="cp">    $curebit = new curebit_checkout();</span>
<span class="cp">    echo $curebit-&gt;getOutput((int)$customer_id);</span>
<span class="cp">  }</span>
<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- End Curebit integration code --&gt;</span>

<span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="cp">  require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;template_bottom.php&#39;);</span>
<span class="cp">  require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;application_bottom.php&#39;);</span>
<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</li>
<li><p class="first">For <strong>version 2.2</strong>, in your catalog directory, edit <em>checkout_success.php</em>
and replace this code:</p>
<div class="highlight-html"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="c">&lt;!-- right_navigation //--&gt;</span>
<span class="cp">&lt;?php require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;column_right.php&#39;); ?&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- right_navigation_eof //--&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;/tr&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/table&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- body_eof //--&gt;</span>

<span class="c">&lt;!-- footer //--&gt;</span>
<span class="cp">&lt;?php require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;footer.php&#39;); ?&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- footer_eof //--&gt;</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
<p>With this code:</p>
<div class="highlight-html"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="c">&lt;!-- right_navigation //--&gt;</span>
<span class="cp">&lt;?php require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;column_right.php&#39;); ?&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- right_navigation_eof //--&gt;</span>
    <span class="nt">&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;/tr&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/table&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- Begin Curebit integration code --&gt;</span>
<span class="cp">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="cp">  include(DIR_WS_MODULES . &#39;order_total/curebit_checkout.php&#39;);</span>
<span class="cp">  if (class_exists(&#39;curebit_checkout&#39;)) {</span>
<span class="cp">    $curebit = new curebit_checkout();</span>
<span class="cp">    echo $curebit-&gt;getOutput((int)$customer_id);</span>
<span class="cp">  }</span>
<span class="cp">?&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- End Curebit integration code --&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- body_eof //--&gt;</span>

<span class="c">&lt;!-- footer //--&gt;</span>
<span class="cp">&lt;?php require(DIR_WS_INCLUDES . &#39;footer.php&#39;); ?&gt;</span>
<span class="c">&lt;!-- footer_eof //--&gt;</span>
</pre></div>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Login to your administrator console (eg <a class="reference external" href="http://yourstoredomain.com/admin">http://yourstoredomain.com/admin</a>)
with your administrator credentials.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click on <strong>Modules</strong> &rarr; <strong>Order Total</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>Install Module</strong> (osCommerce 2.3 only).</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click on the Curebit Checkout <strong>Install</strong> or <strong>Install Module</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>Edit</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Enter your Curebit Site ID. You can get this from your Curebit dashboard
after you log in and create a site.</p>
</li>
<li><p class="first">Click <strong>Save</strong> (or <strong>Update</strong>).</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p><br></p>
<p><a class="reference internal" href="../verify.html#ecommerce-verify"><em>Verifying Integration Instructions</em></a></p>
